  m_text: "Special Cards (Action Cards)\n\nSkip: The next player loses their turn.\n\nReverse:
    The direction of play flips (Clockwise \u2194 Counter-clockwise).\n\nDraw Two:
    The next player draws 2 cards and is skipped.\n\nWild: Change the active color
    to anything you want."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
